tika.dc.description: Managing the Narcissist in Your Life is the first workbook to empower readers with practical solutions for dealing with self-absorbed and narcissistic individuals. It offers essential skills for managing narcissistic behavior in love relationships, the workplace, and in friend and family relationships.
